{
  "stem": "95.3",
  "chunk_idx": 14,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "And the ones who could not go on to the train fast enough, which I did, they were killed.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "I mean, we arrived in Buchenwald after walking those six miles late at night, 1,200 from 4,000.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "Those are the ones who survived during those not even three weeks.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "And we arrived.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "They put us into shower rooms.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "It's too late if I-- and I don't know.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "And I said to my friend there-- I got lost with the other guy-- and I said to my friend, let's not go into the shower room.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "You know, let's-- let's stay in the anteroom.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "If they don't come out after 10 minutes, we'll be next.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "Now, we slept all night long there, because they didn't-- they didn't want to delouse us and disinfect us until the morning, which they did.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "They did not kill us there.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "Buchenwald was a tremendous camp.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "It's the-- it's the biggest one I've seen.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "They had the big camp and they had a little camp.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "And the big camp was constructed in 1937.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "And there were very few Jews at that time in 1937, because they were all sent, after this, to Poland and Upper Silesia.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 46,
      "text": "But when I arrived in '45, they were mostly underground fighters, communist, political people, Russian soldiers in their own compound, Ukrainians, homosexuals, gypsies, Jehovah's Witnesses.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 47,
      "text": "And the Jews were sent into the little camp where they had experimental barracks, where they had a theater.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 48,
      "text": "They had a whorehouse, they had a hospital.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 49,
      "text": "And in Buchenwald, the very famous Ilse Koch.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 50,
      "text": "I don't know if you know what she was doing in Buchenwald.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 51,
      "text": "I mean, I did not know when I was there.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 52,
      "text": "Ilse Koch, outside of the camp-- just outside the barbed wire-- had a zoo, with six bears.",
      "word_count": 17
    }
  ],
